Create a dedicated Guest role environment focused on product discovery, scientific education, and purchasing.

GOAL

Provide non-registered users with a professional scientific storefront experience that supports learning, product selection, and purchasing.

Focus on:

- Scientific Product Search
- Protocol Discovery
- Product Pages
- Cart & Checkout
- Education Hub

Do not enable advanced clinical or logistics tools.

